    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feel without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
