    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its flawless original paint which is further protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creases, and the 'new car' scent lingers. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the panoramic sunroof, functions perfectly. With a full, documented service history from the authorized dealer and zero curb rash on the 21-inch alloy wheels, this is a rare find for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection without the wait of a new factory order.",
      "price": 48500.0,
