    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and meticulously maintained. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a road trip today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat. Can't wait to see who gets to drive this gem home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
