    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies with a staggering 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Variable M Differential Lock, the drivetrain performance is surgical. This vehicle has undergone exhaustive preventative maintenance: the VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, and VAC Motorsports rod bearings have been installed to ensure peak reciprocating assembly health. Furthermore, the rear subframe has been reinforced, eliminating the chassis's inherent structural fatigue points. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers. The exterior retains original factory paint depth, and the Nappa leather interior remains supple with no bolster compression. A turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
